text: Danielle Christine Fishel (born May 5, 1981) is an American actress and television personality. She is best known for starring in the television sitcom Boy Meets World, as well as it's 2014 successor "Girl Meets World" She has also been in several movies. In August 2024, Fishel announced that she had been diagnosed with breast cancer. ==References== Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American television personalities Category:People from Mesa, Arizona Category:Actors from Arizona Category:1981 births Category:Living people
